	<ThingDef ParentName="DE_FungalNexusCraftableBase">
		<defName>DE_PsychicCoordinator</defName>
		<label>psychic coordinator</label>
		<description>A fungal collective relies deeply on psychic connections to function, sharing thoughts instantaneously over long distances. By using archotech shards, it is possible to manually improve these connections. This improves the work speed of the collective, but also how fast the nexus can produce burrowers. This can be installed up to 3 times.</description>
